Class Search Tool

The Class Search Tool is for class schedule planning purposes only. To register for classes, please use Schedule Builder

Future term class schedule information will be available prior to the beginning of Pass I Registration for the term. Please check the Academic Calendar for registration dates.

See our help page for details about the Class Search Tool.

IMPORTANT: Classes are subject to change. Students should verify class information prior to registration and attending classes. For Fall term, the number of "Open" seats includes both seats available to all students and any reserved seats that may be available during the Pass One registration.

Be sure to review with your advisor all GE requirements, Notes and Additional Conditions before choosing courses to fulfill your General Education unit requirements, especially those related to Entry Level Writing and English Composition requirements.
